descript.abstract: Census tracts for Delaware, from the 2010 TIGER shapefiles collection, with population and housing unit counts from the 2010 Census Redistricting Data (Public Law 94-171) Summary File.
descript.purpose: For use in planning and economic development applications. or any other applications that can make use of population and housing unit counts.
